<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f6f9fc; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    h2 { color: #2b7a0b; }
    .status-badge { background: #e8f5e9; color: #2b7a0b; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; }
    th, td { padding: 10px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
    th { background-color: #f3f3f3; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; background: #2b7a0b; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Great news, {{name}}!</h2>
    <p>Your order <strong>#{{order.id}}</strong> has been shipped and is on its way to you.</p>
    
    <div class="status-badge">Status: SHIPPED</div>

    <p>We have attached your official invoice (PDF) to this email for your records.</p>

    <h3>Items in this shipment:</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Product</th>
          <th>Qty</th>
          <th>Total</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each order.items}}
        <tr>
          <td>{{this.product.name}}</td>
          <td>{{this.quantity}}</td>
          <td>TK {{this.price}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p><strong>Grand Total:</strong> TK {{order.totalAmount}}</p>

    <a href="{{appUrl}}/orders/my" class="button">Track Shipment</a>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for shopping with us!<br/><strong>Bamboo Shop Team</strong></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>